{"id": 5337, "title": "Ticket #5337: Have ubertickets age out or get cleaned up on the StartD side.", "description": "<blockquote>\nWhen a user is no longer executing jobs, their uberticket and other credentials should be cleaned up.  I'm proposing a \"mark and sweep\" approach.  When the startd notices the last job for a user finish executing, it marks that credential for cleanup and is then responsible for periodically cleaning up the marked files after X minutes.  Anytime a new credential is stored, existing marks are removed.</blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2016-Mar-11 13:10</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=47714\">[47714]</a></span>: Fix Darwin scandir issue. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"tktview?tn=5337\" title=\"Have ubertickets age out or get cleaned up on the StartD side.\">#5337</a></span>  (By zmiller )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2016-Mar-11 11:14</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=47712\">[47712]</a></span>: Hack cmake files to specify correct function signature. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"tktview?tn=5337\" title=\"Have ubertickets age out or get cleaned up on the StartD side.\">#5337</a></span>  (By zmiller )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2016-Mar-10 16:49</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=47700\">[47700]</a></span>: Fix incorrect function signature on Mac. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"tktview?tn=5337\" title=\"Have ubertickets age out or get cleaned up on the StartD side.\">#5337</a></span>  (By zmiller )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2015-Oct-23 21:08</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=46100\">[46100]</a></span>: Consolidate code for clearing \"mark\" files. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"tktview?tn=5336\" title=\"Have ubertickets age out or get cleaned up on the SchedD side.\">#5336</a></span> <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"tktview?tn=5337\" title=\"Have ubertickets age out or get cleaned up on the StartD side.\">#5337</a></span>  (By zmiller )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2015-Oct-23 19:39</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=46096\">[46096]</a></span>: Implement \"mark and sweep\" for credential expiration on the execute side. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"tktview?tn=5337\" title=\"Have ubertickets age out or get cleaned up on the StartD side.\">#5337</a></span>  (By zmiller )</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>", "type": "enhance", "last_change": "2016-Apr-26 20:52", "status": "resolved", "created": "2015-Oct-22 16:53", "fixed_version": "2015-Oct-22 16:53", "broken_version": "", "priority": "1", "subsystem": "Security", "assigned_to": "zmiller", "derived_from": "#5272", "creator": "zmiller", "rust": "", "customer_group": "cern", "visibility": "public", "notify": "zmiller@cs.wisc.edu, tannenba@cs.wisc.edu", "due_date": "20151029"}